{"tid":2326595,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"big big shop在落單後26天才送到，TVB 賴第三方物流","createTime":"2020-12-15T12:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T15:36:39.000Z","uid":212876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4afc94806035137f2d54c992ba2ab6fc7c97128d","tid":2326595,"uid":212876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"係咪應該幫輕下佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBig Big Shop回覆消委會表示，物流公司並未有完全跟隨公司的包裝及配送指引，導致商品狀態欠佳，11月中開始已更換另一物流公司。<br />\n<br />\n母公司TVB今日拒絕回應《蘋果》查詢，但回覆其他傳媒及在官網發聲明，就引起消費者不便致歉，解釋商品配送由商戶直送或第三方物流公司負責，今年因疫情網購需求上升，Big Big Shop銷售量按年急增5倍，令商戶及物流公司面對巨大壓力引致配送延誤及狀態欠理想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/PNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FPNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGBq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=3fa5d83a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FPNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU%2F&h=03b52651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/PNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU/</a>"},{"pid":"c27e5905b113795d00b006de5e20d340393c45fb","tid":2326595,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23fac5460a009beb095e1998d0267727c1d492c","tid":2326595,"uid":149653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"On9先用Big Big Shop, 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}